msgid ""
"For students to enroll in this course via direct login, you will need to "
"provide them two things"
msgstr "Damit Studierende sich in Ihrem Kurs anmelden können, benötigen sie"

#: admin/actions.php:924 admin/actions.php:926 admin/actions.php:929
#: admin/actions.php:938 admin/actions.php:946 admin/actions.php:950
#: admin/actions.php:1016 admin/actions.php:1018 admin/actions.php:1028
msgid "The course ID"
msgstr "Kurs-ID"

#: admin/actions.php:926 admin/actions.php:928 admin/actions.php:931
#: admin/actions.php:940 admin/actions.php:948 admin/actions.php:952
#: admin/actions.php:1018 admin/actions.php:1020 admin/actions.php:1030
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Tell them to leave the enrollment key blank, since you didn't specify one.  "
"The enrollment key acts like a course password to prevent random strangers "
"from enrolling in your course.  If you want to set an enrollment key, %s "
"modify your course settings %s"
msgstr ""
"Sagen Sie ihnen, dass sie das Feld für das Kurs-Passwort leer lassen sollen. "
"Wenn Sie ein Kurspasswort setzen wollen, so ändern Sie Ihre %s "
"Kurseinstellungen %s"

#: admin/actions.php:928 admin/actions.php:930 admin/actions.php:933
#: admin/actions.php:942 admin/actions.php:950 admin/actions.php:954
#: admin/actions.php:1020 admin/actions.php:1022 admin/actions.php:1032
msgid "The enrollment key"
msgstr "Das Kurs-Passwort"

#: admin/actions.php:933 admin/actions.php:935 admin/actions.php:938
#: admin/actions.php:947 admin/actions.php:955 admin/actions.php:959
#: admin/actions.php:1025 admin/actions.php:1027 admin/actions.php:1037
msgid ""
"If you plan to integrate this course with your school's Learning Management "
"System (LMS), "
msgstr ""
"Wenn Sie diesen Kurs in das Lernmanagement-System (LMS) Ihrer Einrichtung "
"integrieren wollen, "

#: admin/actions.php:935 admin/actions.php:937 admin/actions.php:940
#: admin/actions.php:949 admin/actions.php:957 admin/actions.php:961
#: admin/actions.php:1027 admin/actions.php:1029 admin/actions.php:1039
msgid ""
"it looks like your school may already have a school-wide LTI key and secret "
"established - check with your LMS admin. "
msgstr ""
"es sieht so aus, als ob Ihre Einrichtung Schlüssel (Key) und Passwort "
"(Secret) für die LTI-Verbindung bereits für alle eingerichtet hat - setzen "
"Sie sich mit dem Administrator Ihres LMS in Verbindung. "

#: admin/actions.php:936 admin/forms.php:424 admin/forms.php:870
#: admin/forms.php:456 admin/forms.php:902 admin/actions.php:938
#: admin/forms.php:903 admin/actions.php:941 admin/forms.php:906
#: admin/actions.php:950 admin/forms.php:472 admin/forms.php:936
#: admin/actions.php:958 admin/forms.php:946 admin/actions.php:962
#: admin/forms.php:473 admin/forms.php:947 admin/actions.php:1028
#: admin/forms.php:514 admin/forms.php:995 admin/actions.php:1030
#: admin/actions.php:1040 admin/forms.php:526 admin/forms.php:1014
msgid "If so, you will not need to set up a course-level configuration. "
msgstr ""
"Wenn das so ist, brauchen Sie es nicht mehr auf Kursebene zu konfigurieren. "

#: admin/actions.php:937 admin/actions.php:939 admin/actions.php:942
#: admin/actions.php:951 admin/actions.php:959 admin/actions.php:963
#: admin/actions.php:1029 admin/actions.php:1031 admin/actions.php:1041
msgid ""
"If you do need to set up a course-level configuration for some reason, the "
"key and secret can be found in your course settings"
msgstr ""
"Wenn Sie eine Konfiguration auf Kursebene benötigen, so finden Sie Schlüssel "
"(Key) und Passwort (Secret) für die LTI-Verbindung in Ihren Kurseinstellungen"

#: admin/actions.php:939 admin/actions.php:941 admin/actions.php:944
#: admin/actions.php:953 admin/actions.php:961 admin/actions.php:965
#: admin/actions.php:1031 admin/actions.php:1033 admin/actions.php:1043
msgid ""
"here is the information you will need to set up a course-level "
"configuration, since your school does not appear to have a school-wide LTI "
"key and secret established."
msgstr ""
"so ist hier die Information, die Sie benötigen um die LTI-Verbindung auf "
"Kursebene zu konfigurieren, da Ihre Einrichtung anscheinend Schlüssel (Key) "
"und Passwort (Secret) nicht global eingerichtet hat."

#: admin/actions.php:942 admin/actions.php:944 admin/actions.php:947
#: admin/actions.php:956 admin/actions.php:964 admin/actions.php:968
#: admin/actions.php:1034 admin/actions.php:1036 admin/actions.php:1046
msgid ""
"If you forget these later, you can find them by viewing your course settings."
msgstr ""
"Wenn Sie dies später vergessen, so finden Sie die Informationen in Ihren "
"Kurseinstellungen."

