#: admin/forms.php:1221
msgid "Promote Course"
msgstr "Kurs ankündigen"

#: admin/forms.php:1061 admin/forms.php:1059 admin/forms.php:1091
#: admin/forms.php:1092 admin/forms.php:1095 admin/forms.php:1135
#: admin/forms.php:1145 admin/forms.php:1146 admin/forms.php:1198
#: admin/forms.php:1224
msgid "Promote in Course Browser"
msgstr "In der Kursübersicht veröffentlichen"

#: admin/forms.php:1063 admin/forms.php:1061 admin/forms.php:1093
#: admin/forms.php:1094 admin/forms.php:1097 admin/forms.php:1137
#: admin/forms.php:1147 admin/forms.php:1148 admin/forms.php:1200
#: admin/forms.php:1226
msgid "Course Browser Settings"
msgstr "Einstellungen für Kursübersicht"

#: admin/forms.php:1064 admin/forms.php:1062 admin/forms.php:1094
#: admin/forms.php:1095 admin/forms.php:1098 admin/forms.php:1138
#: admin/forms.php:1148 admin/forms.php:1149 admin/forms.php:1201
#: admin/forms.php:1227
msgid ""
"Promoting your course will advertise it to all users of this system, making "
"it easy for them to copy this course."
msgstr ""
"Wenn Sie Ihren Kurs veröffentlichen, so kann er von allen Benutzern gefunden "
"und von Dozenten kopiert werden."

#: admin/forms.php:1065 admin/forms.php:1063 admin/forms.php:1095
#: admin/forms.php:1096 admin/forms.php:1099 admin/forms.php:1139
#: admin/forms.php:1149 admin/forms.php:1150 admin/forms.php:1202
#: admin/forms.php:1228
msgid ""
"You should only promote a course that is complete and ready to share with "
"the world."
msgstr "Sie sollten nur fertige Kurse veröffentlichen."

#: admin/forms.php:1066 admin/forms.php:1064 admin/forms.php:1096
#: admin/forms.php:1097 admin/forms.php:1100 admin/forms.php:1140
#: admin/forms.php:1150 admin/forms.php:1151 admin/forms.php:1203
#: admin/forms.php:1229
msgid ""
"Before sharing your course, check to ensure that it only contains materials "
"you created or have the rights to share."
msgstr ""
"Bevor Sie einen Kurs veröffentlichen prüfen Sie bitte, dass er nur Material "
"enthält, dass Sie mit anderen teilen dürfen."

#: admin/forms.php:1067 admin/forms.php:1065 admin/forms.php:1097
#: admin/forms.php:1098 admin/forms.php:1101 admin/forms.php:1141
#: admin/forms.php:1151 admin/forms.php:1152 admin/forms.php:1204
#: admin/forms.php:1230
msgid ""
"Your course should contain no commercial, copyrighted content, including "
"textbook pages, activites, test bank items, etc."
msgstr ""
"Ihr Kurs sollte keine kommerziellen oder Copyright-geschützte Inhalte "
"enthalten, wie Seiten aus Lehrbüchern, Aktivitäten, Testsätze, u.s.w."

#: admin/forms.php:1068 admin/forms.php:1066 admin/forms.php:1098
#: admin/forms.php:1099 admin/forms.php:1102 admin/forms.php:1142
#: admin/forms.php:1152 admin/forms.php:1153 admin/forms.php:1205
#: admin/forms.php:1231
msgid ""
"Openly licensed material, clearly marked with an open license, is fine to "
"include."
msgstr ""
"Material, das deutlich mit einer freien Lizenz versehen ist, darf im Kurs "
"vorkommen."

#: admin/forms.php:1069 admin/forms.php:1067 admin/forms.php:1099
#: admin/forms.php:1100 admin/forms.php:1103 admin/forms.php:1143
#: admin/forms.php:1153 admin/forms.php:1154 admin/forms.php:1206
#: admin/forms.php:1232
msgid ""
"If sharing your own materials (textbook, activities, paper assessments), "
"please mark the materials with an open license, or include a blanket license "
"statement somewhere in the course."
msgstr ""
"Wenn Sie eigenes Material (Lehrbuch, Aktivitäten, Papiertests) weitergeben, "
"so kennzeichnen Sie dieses bitte mit einer offenen Lizenz  oder fügen eine "
"Lizenz an geeigneter Stelle in den Kurs ein."

