#: course/addassessment2form.php:716 course/addassessment2form.php:718
#: course/addassessment2form.php:720 course/addassessment2form.php:724
#: course/addassessment2form.php:731 course/addassessment2form.php:732
#: course/addassessment2form.php:780 course/addassessment2form.php:792
msgid "Display Styles"
msgstr "Darstellungsarten"

#: course/addassessment2form.php:729 course/addassessment2form.php:731
#: course/addassessment2form.php:733 course/addassessment2form.php:737
#: course/addassessment2form.php:744 course/addassessment2form.php:745
#: course/addassessment2form.php:793 course/addassessment2form.php:805
msgid ""
"Students will see one question at a time, and can jump between them in any "
"order"
msgstr ""
"Die Studierenden sehen jede Frage einzeln und können beliebig zwischen ihnen "
"wechseln"

#: course/addassessment2form.php:730 course/addassessment2form.php:732
#: course/addassessment2form.php:734 course/addassessment2form.php:738
#: course/addassessment2form.php:745 course/addassessment2form.php:746
#: course/addassessment2form.php:794 course/addassessment2form.php:806
msgid ""
"In this style,\tstudents will typically see all the questions on the screen "
"at once. If desired, you can break the questions into pages on the Add/"
"Remove Questions page by clicking the +Text button and selecting the New "
"Page option."
msgstr ""
"Dabei sehen die Studierenden i. Allg. alle Fragen gleichzeitig auf dem "
"Bildschirm Sie können die Fragen bei der Zusammenstellung des Tests auch auf "
"mehrere Seiten verteilen. Klicken Sie für den Beginn einer neuen Seite auf "
"die +-Text-Schaltfläche und wählen Sie die Option \"Neue Seite\"."

#: course/addassessment2form.php:731 course/addassessment2form.php:733
#: course/addassessment2form.php:735 course/addassessment2form.php:739
#: course/addassessment2form.php:746 course/addassessment2form.php:747
#: course/addassessment2form.php:795 course/addassessment2form.php:807
msgid ""
"In this style, the questions pop up automatically at specified times while "
"watching a YouTube video. On the Add/Remove Questions page, after adding the "
"questions to the assessment, click Define Video Cues to specify the video "
"and times to display the\tquestions."
msgstr ""
"Bei dieser Darstellung sehen die Studierenden ein YouTube-Video. An "
"bestimmten Stellen wird die Wiedergabe des Videos durch Fragen des Tests "
"unterbrochen. Nachdem Sie die Fragen für den Test zusammengestellt haben "
"klicken Sie auf \"In Video einordnen\" um das Video und die Zeiten, an denen "
"es durch Ihre Fragen unterbrochen wird, festzulegen."

#: course/addassessment2form.php:733 course/addassessment2form.php:735
#: course/addassessment2form.php:737 course/addassessment2form.php:741
#: course/addassessment2form.php:748 course/addassessment2form.php:749
#: course/addassessment2form.php:797 course/addassessment2form.php:809
msgid "LivePoll"
msgstr "Live-Umfrage"

#: course/addassessment2form.php:733 course/addassessment2form.php:735
#: course/addassessment2form.php:737 course/addassessment2form.php:741
#: course/addassessment2form.php:748 course/addassessment2form.php:749
#: course/addassessment2form.php:797 course/addassessment2form.php:809
msgid ""
"This is a clicker-style display, requiring students to be in the assessment "
"at the same time as the teacher. The teacher opens a question for students "
"to answer, and results can be viewed live as they are submitted."
msgstr ""
"Für diese Darstellungsart sollten sich Studierende und Dozent in einem Raum "
"befinden, z.B. in einer Vorlesung. Der Dozent gibt die Fragen einzeln für "
"die Studierenden frei, die sie auf ihren Computern bearbeiten. Einzelne "
"Ergebnisse werden dem Dozenten angezeigt sobald sie eingehen."

#: course/addassessment2form.php:749 course/chgassessments2form.php:749
#: course/addassessment2form.php:751 course/chgassessments2form.php:761
#: course/addassessment2form.php:753 course/chgassessments2form.php:763
#: course/addassessment2form.php:757 course/addassessment2form.php:764
#: course/chgassessments2form.php:772 course/addassessment2form.php:765
#: course/chgassessments2form.php:773 course/addassessment2form.php:813
#: course/chgassessments2form.php:828 course/addassessment2form.php:825
#: course/chgassessments2form.php:841
msgid "On each question immediately"
msgstr "Sofort bei jeder Frage"

#: course/addassessment2form.php:753 course/chgassessments2form.php:753
#: course/addassessment2form.php:755 course/chgassessments2form.php:765
#: course/addassessment2form.php:757 course/chgassessments2form.php:767
