msgstr "Fragen im Test"

#: course/addquestions.php:1222 course/addquestions.php:1239
#: course/addquestions.php:1247 course/addquestions.php:1250
#: course/addquestions2.php:525 course/addquestions.php:1260
#: course/addquestions2.php:530 course/addquestions2.php:531
