msgstr "Test hat keine Fragen"

#: course/addquestions.php:1226 course/addquestions.php:1243
#: course/addquestions.php:1251 course/addquestions.php:1254
#: course/addquestions2.php:529 course/addquestions.php:1264
#: course/addquestions2.php:534 course/addquestions2.php:535
#: course/addquestions.php:1265 course/addquestions2.php:536
#: course/addquestions.php:1271 course/addquestions2.php:545
#: course/addquestions.php:1273 course/addquestions2.php:546
msgid "How do I find questions to add?"
msgstr "Wo kann ich Fragen für den Test finden?"

#: course/addquestions.php:1229 course/addquestions.php:1246
#: course/addquestions.php:1254 course/addquestions.php:1257
#: course/addquestions.php:1267 course/addquestions.php:1268
#: course/addquestions.php:1274 course/addquestions.php:1276
msgid ""
"You are currently set to select questions from the question libraries.  If "
"you would like to select questions from assessments you've already created, "
"click the <b>Select From Assessments</b> button below"
msgstr ""
"Sie fügen Fragen aus der Fragen-Bibliothek hinzu. Wenn Sie lieber Fragen aus "
"Tests nehmen wollen, die Sie früher angelegt haben, so wählen Sie unten "
"<b>Auswahl aus Tests</b>"

#: course/addquestions.php:1230 course/addquestions.php:1247
#: course/addquestions.php:1255 course/addquestions.php:1258
#: course/addquestions.php:1268 course/addquestions.php:1269
#: course/addquestions.php:1275 course/addquestions.php:1277
msgid "To find questions to add from the question libraries:"
msgstr "Um Fragen aus der Fragen-Bibliothek zu finden:"

#: course/addquestions.php:1231 course/addquestions.php:1248
#: course/addquestions.php:1256 course/addquestions.php:1259
#: course/addquestions.php:1269 course/addquestions.php:1270
#: course/addquestions.php:1276 course/addquestions.php:1278
msgid ""
"Click the <b>Select Libraries</b> button below to pop open the library "
"selector"
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie unten auf <b>Bibliotheken auswählen</b> um die "
"Bibliotheksauswahl zu öffnen"

#: course/addquestions.php:1232 course/addquestions.php:1249
#: course/addquestions.php:1257 course/addquestions.php:1260
#: course/addquestions.php:1270 course/addquestions.php:1271
#: course/addquestions.php:1277 course/addquestions.php:1279
msgid ""
"In the library selector, open up the topics of interest, and click the "
"checkbox to select libraries to use"
msgstr ""
"In der Bibliotheksauswahl öffnen klicken Sie auf die Kontrollkästchen der "
"Unterbibliotheken, die Sie interessieren"

#: course/addquestions.php:1233 course/addquestions.php:1250
#: course/addquestions.php:1258 course/addquestions.php:1261
#: course/addquestions.php:1271 course/addquestions.php:1272
#: course/addquestions.php:1278 course/addquestions.php:1280
msgid ""
"Scroll down in the library selector, and click the <b>Use Libraries</b> "
"button"
msgstr ""
"Scrollen Sie in der Bibliotheksauswahl nach unten unt klicken Sie auf die "
"Schaltfläche <b>Bibliotheken verwenden</b>"

#: course/addquestions.php:1234 course/addquestions.php:1251
#: course/addquestions.php:1259 course/addquestions.php:1262
#: course/addquestions.php:1272 course/addquestions.php:1273
#: course/addquestions.php:1279 course/addquestions.php:1281
msgid ""
"On this page, click the <b>Search</b> button to list the questions in the "
"libraries selected.<br/>  You can limit the listing by entering a sepecific "
"search term in the box provided first, or leave it blank to view all "
"questions in the chosen libraries"
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf dieser Seite auf die <b>Suchen</b>-Schaltfläche um die "
"Fragen in den ausgewählten Bibliotheken anzuzeigen.</br> Sie können die "
"Suche durch Eingabe eines spezifischen Suchbegriffs im ersten Eingabefeld "
"eingrenzen oder dieses Feld ler lassen, um alle Fragen in den gewählten "
"Bibliotheken zu sehen"

#: course/addquestions.php:1237 course/addquestions.php:1254
#: course/addquestions.php:1262 course/addquestions.php:1265
#: course/addquestions.php:1275 course/addquestions.php:1276
#: course/addquestions.php:1282 course/addquestions.php:1284
msgid ""
"You are currently set to select questions existing assessments.  If you "
"would like to select questions from the question libraries, click the "
"<b>Select From Libraries</b> button below"
msgstr ""
"Sie wollen Fragen aus anderen Tests wählen. Wenn Sie lieber Fragen aus der "
"Fragen-Bibliothek wählen möchten, so klicken Sie unten auf die Schaltfläche "
"<b>Aus Bibliothek auswählen</b>"

#: course/addquestions.php:1238 course/addquestions.php:1255
#: course/addquestions.php:1263 course/addquestions.php:1266
#: course/addquestions.php:1276 course/addquestions.php:1277
#: course/addquestions.php:1283 course/addquestions.php:1285
msgid "To find questions to add from existing assessments:"
msgstr "Um Fragen aus anderen Tests zu finden, die Sie hinzufügen können:"

#: course/addquestions.php:1239 course/addquestions.php:1256
#: course/addquestions.php:1264 course/addquestions.php:1267
#: course/addquestions.php:1277 course/addquestions.php:1278
#: course/addquestions.php:1284 course/addquestions.php:1286
msgid ""
"Use the checkboxes to select the assessments you want to pull questions from"
msgstr ""
"Markieren Sie die Kontrollkästchen um die Tests auszuwählen, aus denen Sie "
"Fragen übernehmen möchten"

#: course/addquestions.php:1240 course/addquestions.php:1257
#: course/addquestions.php:1265 course/addquestions.php:1268
#: course/addquestions.php:1278 course/addquestions.php:1279
#: course/addquestions.php:1285 course/addquestions.php:1287
msgid ""
"Click <b>Use these Assessments</b> button to list the questions in the "
"assessments selected"
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf die Schaltfläche <b>Diese Tests verwenden</b> um die Fragen "
"in den ausgewählten Tests anzuzeigen"

#: course/addquestions.php:1243 course/addquestions.php:1260
#: course/addquestions.php:1268 course/addquestions.php:1271
#: course/addquestions2.php:543 course/addquestions.php:1281
#: course/addquestions2.php:548 course/addquestions2.php:549
#: course/addquestions.php:1282 course/addquestions2.php:550
#: course/addquestions.php:1288 course/addquestions2.php:559
#: course/addquestions.php:1290 course/addquestions2.php:560
msgid "To select questions and add them:"
msgstr "Um Fragen auszuwählen und hinzuzufügen:"

#: course/addquestions.php:1244 course/addquestions.php:1261
#: course/addquestions.php:1269 course/addquestions.php:1272
#: course/addquestions.php:1282 course/addquestions.php:1283
#: course/addquestions.php:1289 course/addquestions.php:1291
msgid ""
"Click the <b>Preview</b> button after the question description to view an "
"example of the question"
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf die <b>Vorschau</b>-Schaltfläche neben der Beschreibung um "
"ein Beispiel der Frage zu sehen"

#: course/addquestions.php:1245 course/addquestions.php:1262
#: course/addquestions.php:1270 course/addquestions.php:1273
#: course/addquestions2.php:545 course/addquestions.php:1283
#: course/addquestions2.php:550 course/addquestions2.php:551
#: course/addquestions.php:1284 course/addquestions2.php:552
#: course/addquestions.php:1290 course/addquestions2.php:561
#: course/addquestions.php:1292 course/addquestions2.php:562
msgid "Use the checkboxes to mark the questions you want to use"
msgstr ""
"Verwenden Sie die Kontrollkästchen um die Fragen auszuwählen, die Sie "
"verwenden möchten"

#: course/addquestions.php:1246 course/addquestions.php:1263
#: course/addquestions.php:1271 course/addquestions.php:1274
#: course/addquestions.php:1284 course/addquestions.php:1285
#: course/addquestions.php:1291 course/addquestions.php:1293
msgid ""
"Click the <b>Add</b> button above the question list to add the questions to "
"your assessment"
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf die Schaltfläche <b>Hinzufügen</b> über der Fragenliste, um "
"die Fragen zu Ihrem Test hinzuzufügen"

