msgid "Load Video"
msgstr "Video laden"

#: course/addvideotimes.php:399 course/addvideotimes.php:403
#: course/addvideotimes.php:417
msgid "Video Aspect Ratio:"
msgstr "Seitenverhältnis des Videos:"

