#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:162 course/gb-rescoreq.php:213
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:215 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:55
#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:57 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:56
#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:58 course/gb-rescoreq.php:163
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:214 course/gb-rescoreq.php:216
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:170 course/gb-rescoreq.php:221
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:223
msgid "Regrade Question"
msgstr "Bewertung der Frage überprüfen"

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:163 course/gb-rescoreq.php:164
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:171
msgid "Please be patient - this page will auto-submit when it is done loading"
msgstr ""
"Bitte haben Sie etwas Geduld - Diese Seite wird aktualisiert, wenn Sie "
"fertig geladen ist"

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:220 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:62
#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:63 course/gb-rescoreq.php:221
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:228
msgid "This will allow you rescore this question. "
msgstr "Dies erlaubt eine neue Bewertung der Antwort. "

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:221 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:63
#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:64 course/gb-rescoreq.php:222
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:229
msgid "This is intended to be used after fixing a bug in the question code. "
msgstr ""
"Dies wird verwendet, nachdem ein Problem im Code der Frage korrigiert wurde. "

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:222 course/gb-rescoreq.php:223
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:230
msgid ""
"This page will re-submit the student's answer to their best-scored version "
"of this question (the latest version if all are 0), scoring it as if it was "
"their first attempt. "
msgstr ""
"Diese Seite wird die Antwort der Studierenden erneut als am Besten bewertete "
"Version einreichen (als jüngste Version, wenn alle 0 sind). Sie wird so "
"bewertet, als ob es der erste Versuch ist. "

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:223 course/gb-rescoreq.php:224
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:231
msgid ""
"This process will wipe out all record of other attempts the student made on "
"this question, and reset their attempt count to 1 on this question. "
msgstr ""
"Dies löscht alle Daten über andere Versuche des Studenten zu dieser Frage. "
"Die Anzahl der bisher gemachten Versuche dieser Frage wird auf 1 "
"zurückgesetzt. "

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:225 course/gb-rescoreq.php:226
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:233
msgid "Which answer from the student do you want to resubmit?"
msgstr "Welche Antwort möchten Sie neu einreichen?"

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:227 course/gb-rescoreq.php:228
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:235
msgid ""
"The first attempt. Recommended for single-part questions, to rescore the "
"student's first try."
msgstr ""
"Die erste Antwort. Empfohlen für Fragen mit einem Teil um den ersten Versuch "
"des Studenten neu zu bewerten."

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:229 course/gb-rescoreq.php:230
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:237
msgid ""
"The last attempt. Recommended for multi-part questions, to preserve the "
"score on working parts."
msgstr ""
"Der letzte Versuch. Empfohlen für Multipart-Fragen, um die Punkte der "
"bereits bearbeiteten Teile zu erhalten."

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:231 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:73
#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:74 course/gb-rescoreq.php:232
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:239
msgid "Are you SURE you want to proceed?"
msgstr "Sind Sie SICHER, dass Sie fortsetzen wollen?"

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:232 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:74
#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:75 course/gb-rescoreq.php:233
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:240
msgid "Rescore Question"
msgstr "Punkte der Frage überprüfen"

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:235 course/gb-rescoreq.php:236
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:243
msgid ""
"When you continue, all students' attempts will be loaded up on your screen "
"and then automatically submitted for regrading. "
msgstr ""
"Wenn Sie fortfahren, werden alle Versuche aller Studierenden auf Ihren "
"Bildschirm geladen und automatisch zur erneuten Bewertung eingereicht. "

#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:236 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:77
#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:78 course/gb-rescoreq.php:237
#: course/gb-rescoreq.php:244
msgid "Please be patient - it may take a minute or two"
msgstr "Bitte haben Sie Geduld, das kann ein oder zwei Minuten dauern"

#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:64 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:65
msgid ""
"This page will re-submit the student's answer to this question, scoring it "
"as if it was their first try on that version. This will be repeated for all "
"versions of the assessment or question."
msgstr ""
"Diese Seite wird die Antwort des Studierenden auf diese Frage erneut "
"einreichen. Die Antwort wird so gewertet, als ob sie der erste Versuch zu "
"dieser Frage wäre. Dies wird für alle Versionen des Tests oder der Frage "
"wiederholt."

#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:65 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:66
msgid ""
"This process will wipe out all record of other tries the student made on "
"this question, and reset their try count to 1 on this question. "
msgstr ""
"Dies löscht alle Daten über andere Versuche des Studierenden zu dieser "
"Frage. Die Anzahl der bisherigen Versuche dieser Frage wird auf 1 "
"zurückgesetzt. "

#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:67 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:68
msgid "Which try from the student do you want to resubmit?"
msgstr "Welche Antwort des Studenten möchten Sie erneut einreichen?"

#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:69 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:70
msgid ""
"The first try. Recommended for single-part questions, to rescore the "
"student's first try."
msgstr ""
"Erster Versuch Empfohlen für Fragen mit nur einem Teil um den ersten Versuch "
"des Studierenden neu zu bewerten."

#: course/gb-rescoreq2.php:71 course/gb-rescoreq2.php:72
msgid ""
"The last try. Recommended for multi-part questions, to preserve the score on "
"working parts."
msgstr ""
"Der letzte Versuch. Empfohlen für Multipart-Fragen, um die Punkte der "
"bereits bearbeiteten Teile zu erhalten."

