#: course/gradebook.php:1307 course/gradebook.php:1311
#: course/gradebook.php:1318 course/gradebook.php:1322
#: course/gradebook.php:1327 course/gradebook.php:1345
#: course/gradebook.php:1346 course/gradebook.php:1446
msgid ""
"<dt>Past Due:</dt> <dd>total only includes items whose due date has passed.  "
"Current assignments are not counted in this total."
msgstr ""
"<b>Überfällig</b> Gesamtsumme enthält nur Teile die überfällig sind. "
"Laufende Tests sind dabei nicht berücksichtigt."

#: course/gradebook.php:1310 course/gradebook.php:1314
#: course/gradebook.php:1321 course/gradebook.php:1325
#: course/gradebook.php:1330 course/gradebook.php:1348
#: course/gradebook.php:1349 course/gradebook.php:1449
msgid ""
"<dt>Past Due and Attempted:</dt> <dd> total includes items whose due date "
"has passed, as well as currently available items you have started working on."
msgstr ""
"<b>Überfällig und versucht</b> Gesamtsumme enthält Teile die überfällig "
"sind, sowie verfügbare Teile deren Bearbeitung Sie begonnen haben."

#: course/gradebook.php:1314 course/gradebook.php:1318
#: course/gradebook.php:1325 course/gradebook.php:1329
msgid ""
"<dt>Past Due and Available:</dt> <dd> total includes items whose due date "
"has passed as well as currently available items, even if you haven't "
"starting working on them yet."
msgstr ""
"<b>Überfällig und verfügbar</b> Gesamtsumme enthält Teile die überfällig "
"sind, sowie verfügbare Teile, auch wenn Sie deren Bearbeitung noch nicht "
"begonnen haben."

#: course/gradebook.php:1317 course/gradebook.php:1321
#: course/gradebook.php:1328 course/gradebook.php:1332
#: course/gradebook.php:1337 course/gradebook.php:1355
#: course/gradebook.php:1356 course/gradebook.php:1456
msgid ""
"<dt>All:</dt> <dd> total includes all items: past, current, and future to-be-"
"done items."
msgstr ""
"<b>Alle:</b> Gesamtsumme enthält alle Teile: Vergangene, aktuelle und noch "
"zu erledigende Teile."

