msgid ""
"<dt>Past Due and Available:</dt> <dd> total includes items whose due date "
"has passed as well as currently available items, even if you haven't started "
"working on them yet."
msgstr ""
"<dt>Fällig und verfügbar:</dt> <dd> die Punktzahl berücksichtigt Tests deren "
